Question: EVBOLT CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
EVBOLT

Product: DYNO 11 Electric Vehicle Charger

- Withstands temperatures up to 131°F (55°C)
- Level II AC Charger with 11.5KW power output
- Features a 4.3 inch LCD touchscreen display
- Supports LAN, WIFI, and Cellular Network
- Includes a 2-year worry-free guarantee
- Offers one-year free networking services
- Booth 11123 at CES 2024
- Promotional offers and prizes available at the booth
- Mission to expedite the shift towards electromobility
